          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 优先于 Promise 微任务；浏览器无 nextTick。写异步题时先画「同步 → 微任务 → 宏任务」顺序即可。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "示例："
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "宏任务与微任务交错时的输出顺序。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "console.log(1)\nsetTimeout(() => console.log(2), 0)\nPromise.resolve().then(() => console.log(3))\nconsole.log(4)\n// 输出：1 4 3 2"
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
